channel.title: PLEASE HELP Main class could not find GUI
channel.description: I can't get my DL client to work for others.. It always says main class could not find GUI and many players are trying to play.. Here is my run [code]@echo off start javaw -Xmx500m -cp .;Theme.jar Gui exit [/code] I am using one-scape Delta 317

item.title: PLEASE HELP Main class could not find GUI
item.dc:creator: @mista_pnut mista pnut
item.description:
@mista_pnut wrote:

The main class for deltas isn’t GUI, it’s normally client.

Try and let me know:

@echo off
start javaw -Xmx500m -cp .;Theme.jar client
exit
